20
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:47,160
She is actually waiting?

21
00:03:48,040 --> 00:03:49,040
How inflexible.

22
00:03:54,600 --> 00:03:55,400
No.

23
00:03:57,880 --> 00:04:01,360
Sang Zhan, don't get fooled
by her gentle appearance.

24
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:03,040
All these...

25
00:04:03,240 --> 00:04:04,560
are like sugar coated bullets.

26
