having a candle light dinner with me.

33
00:05:06,560 --> 00:05:07,640
Then why did you come back?

34
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:09,480
I'm done eating, shouldn't I be back?

35
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:12,960
Sang Tian,

36
00:05:13,080 --> 00:05:16,000
I didn't mean to offend you, but
do you know a girl's thought?

37
00:05:16,400 --> 00:05:17,280
[What?]

38
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:19,120
[I'm a girl, okay?]

39
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:23,070
Is it the "straight man cancer" in you?
Xiao Rou took the initiative...

40
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:25,390
to invite you for a candle light dinner.

41
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:27,870
