Imagine that I'm Xiao Rou now.
We just went out for a date,

46
00:05:45,520 --> 00:05:46,560
and we're bidding goodbye.

47
00:05:49,520 --> 00:05:50,640
Tian Tian,

48
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:56,080
