Both of you have been
together for so long,

51
00:06:10,200 --> 00:06:12,880
but you're acting like strangers.
How do you get closer like that?

52
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:14,520
Could it be that...

53
00:06:18,400 --> 00:06:19,600
both of you are siblings?

54
00:06:21,080 --> 00:06:22,520
Who says we are siblings?

55
00:06:22,760 --> 00:06:23,910
She is my girlfriend.

56
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:25,360
Yes. Girlfriend.

57
00:06:25,440 --> 00:06:26,400
Let's do it again then.

58
00:06:35,960 --> 00:06:37,970
Tian Tian,

59
00:06:39,280 --> 00:06:40,920
see you tomorrow.

60
00:06:45,880 --> 00:06:47,800
Are you alright?

61
00:06:50,159 --> 00:06:51,440
You're always being dilly-dally.

62
00:06:51,520 --> 00:06:53,480
That's why your relationship
is not going forward.

63
